commit 66cd49f588bbfac513c1afd41e5d6e92f9b7b833

PMU is not supported (currently) for AvantaLP despite it is armv7 CPU.

Signed-off-by: Kosta Zertsekel <konszert@marvell.com>
Change-Id: Idfb47c57258571e34ea4ec3dcbcda220ddaebee4
